N2  - The article presents information on a study which examined the effects of experience on the performance of managers in the early stages of their careers. Details are presented related to the measures of experience used to predict the performance achieved by managers. A discussion is presented about the dimensions of a managers' job. The author presents an application of multiple regression analysis. The author examines the relationship between managerial experience and organizational effectiveness.
